          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How We Help You Navigate Swiss Immigration</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            <p>
              Our immigration specialists provide comprehensive visa and permit assistance throughout Switzerland. We understand the 
              complexities of Swiss immigration law and offer practical solutions to navigate work permits, residence permits, and 
              family reunification procedures with confidence.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Visa & Work Permit Applications</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Expert support for all permit types</strong> including L permits (short-term), B permits (residence), 
                G permits (cross-border), and C permits (permanent settlement). We handle employer-sponsored applications and quota management.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Residence Permits & Renewals</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Comprehensive support for residence permit applications and timely renewals. We ensure your documentation is complete 
                and submitted at least 3 months before expiry to avoid gaps in legal status.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Family Reunification Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Professional assistance bringing spouses and children to Switzerland. We verify income requirements, housing suitability, 
