                business hub with the highest number of <strong>corporate-sponsored work permits</strong>. The canton processes permits 
                for financial services professionals, tech specialists, and international business executives. Our immigration specialists 
                understand Zurich's cantonal requirements and work closely with employers to secure work permits efficiently. With established 
                <a href="/services/banking-finance" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">banking services</a> and 
                <a href="/services/housing" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">housing support</a>, we provide comprehensive relocation assistance.
              </p>
            </div>

