              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                As Switzerland's federal capital, <a href="/locations/bern" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Bern</a> 
                provides <strong>direct access to national immigration authorities</strong>. The city hosts federal government employees, 
                embassy staff, and international civil servants with specialized permit requirements. Bern's immigration office coordinates 
                with federal departments for complex cases. Our specialists leverage these connections to expedite applications and resolve 
                unique immigration challenges.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step-by-Step Immigration Journey -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Step-by-Step Immigration Journey</h2>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-primary-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <ol class="space-y-6">
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Immigration Assessment</h4>
