              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-gray-800"><strong>Standard processing times:</strong> EU/EFTA 2-4 weeks, third-country nationals 6-12 weeks (updated October 2025)</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-gray-800"><strong>Residence permits (B):</strong> Usually tied to employment contract duration, renewable for 1-5 years depending on nationality</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-gray-800"><strong>Family reunification:</strong> Requires proof of adequate income, suitable housing, and valid residence permit – spouses and children under 18 (or 21 if in education)</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-gray-800"><strong>Renewal timeline:</strong> Start renewal process at least 3 months before permit expiry to avoid gaps in legal status</p>
              </li>
