                registration and receive their residence permit within 2-4 weeks as they don't need prior authorization. <strong>Third-country 
                nationals</strong> typically wait 6-12 weeks for work permit approval, as applications require cantonal and sometimes federal 
                review, plus quota allocation. Applications must be submitted before starting employment. Our specialists expedite the process 
                through proper documentation and direct relationships with cantonal authorities.
              </p>
